descriptor.name: Nestle Ceregrow Grain Selection Ragi Mixed Fruit & Ghee, 300 g (Bag in Box)
descriptor.long_desc: New Ceregrow Grain Selection Growing up cereal with Ragi, Mixed Fruit and Ghee is a toddler cereal inspired by traditional ingredients and popular millet recipes. It contains Nutri Cereal Ragi which has been a part of traditional foods in major parts of India, being grown for over 4000 years in India. Ragi is also locally known by different names like nachni, mandu, keppai, taidalu, finger millet, etc. With over 14 vitamins and minerals and key immune nutrients like vitamins A, C, D, Iron, and Zinc, this cereal helps support normal immune system function. - A tasty bowl of dense nutrition inspired by traditional ingredients for your little one- Made with traditional ingredients like ragi, wheat, milk, and ghee - With 14 minerals and vitamins, it helps support normal immune system function- No added color and flavorAbout the Brand: Nestle has over 150 years of expertise in child nutrition. They are committed to maintaining the highest quality standards that help earn your trust. Their multiple quality checks ensure that they meet organic food's unique requirements, especially meant for your little ones. Nestle has more than 2000 brands ranging from global icons to local favorites and is present in 186 countries worldwide.
